# AGENTS.override.md - plc_or_device_tool

## Profile

plc_or_device_tool

## Purpose

Override base AGENTS.md guidance for PLC, device, equipment, or hardware-adjacent tooling.

## Read Order

1. AGENTS.md
2. AGENTS.override.md
3. PRODUCT.md
4. MVP.md
5. STATUS.md
6. ACCEPTANCE_TRACE.md
7. docs/SAFETY_POLICY.md
8. docs/VERIFICATION.md
9. docs/AI_HANDOFF.md

## Core Rule

Simulator/mock first. Live device write is prohibited by default.

## Allowed Default Work

- Documentation.
- Interface contract review.
- Read-only polling design notes.
- Simulator/mock workflow design.
- Safety and verification planning.

## Prohibited Default Work

- Live device write.
- Start, stop, reset, mode change, or control action.
- Real equipment connection code.
- Repo inclusion of equipment IP, port, tag, address, or live parameter details.
- Secret/config generation.

## P1 Template Boundary

This template does not create device code, PLC code, connection config, tag maps, or live-control scripts.
